text: Oscar Dose (29 March 1901 - 13 October 1988) was a Swedish diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1988 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gothenburg
